{"tid":2112521,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"涉煽惑罪臨急提堂 官下令10萬元保釋 快必：係咪打劫呀？","createTime":"2020-07-17T11:21:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-17T14:07:21.000Z","uid":56115,"like":77,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"9181ddc2026f1ecc221cab7168b8c92f589da4eb","tid":2112521,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T11:21:49.000Z","msg":"人民力量副主席「快必」譚得志今午為網台D100節目錄音後，在數碼港停車場遭警方拘捕，被指於今年1月17日在大埔海濱公園煽惑他人參與由民間集會團隊舉辦的 「天下制裁」流水式集會。快必隨即被帶往粉嶺裁判法院提堂，案件押後10個星期再訊。主任裁判官蘇文隆批准保釋，但要求快必交出10萬元保釋金。快必散庭後不滿謂：「係咪打劫呀？」而庭外有超過10名防暴警員巡邏。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，控方指控「快必」案發當日呼籲市民上街，並發表針對警方的言論，包括「解散警隊，刻不容緩」。案情並透露，集會中有人提及「光復香港，時代革命」的口號，主張探討香港獨立的可行性。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200717/YVSLUUVIWAUMHUS3UESBH6SABE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200717%2FYVSLUUVIWAUMHUS3UESBH6SABE%2F&d=6SBmejzB2pOSQzgprEhHpRD7%2Fo0bOSfVmdYqJtNqH20%3D&h=3acd3e45\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200717%2FYVSLUUVIWAUMHUS3UESBH6SABE%2F&h=a0dd5fe9\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200717/YVSLUUVIWAUMHUS3UESBH6SABE/</a>"},{"pid":"c08b257b84c7569057654b19d7f0117667230e36","tid":2112521,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T11:22:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8204f6d9c7c6c5e65a493f9fdac7da8467db9d5c","tid":2112521,"uid":335434,"like":106,"dislike":1,"score":105,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T11:24:58.000Z","msg":"//主任裁判官<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">蘇文隆</span></strong></span>批准保釋，但要求快必交出10萬元保釋金。快必散庭後不滿謂：「係咪打劫呀？」而庭外有超過10名防暴警員巡邏。//<br />\n<br />\n乜又係你啊 蘇生!?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c243fcef280b645aeb44253fd887549296bc6760","tid":2112521,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T11:25:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets